result.name: 活一鮮

reviews.text: Small Japanese restaurant offering sashimi, udon, tempura, teppanyaki items. Good price, good food, crowded with customers.
Greatest japanese food in sai ying pun. Veryvreasonably priced too. Nuff said.

Delicious sushi around HKU Station (4min walk).  A lot of takeaway request and the queue is always long. The wait for sushi is about 30-45min but worth the wait as it's tasty, a lot variety and good price. 👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻
Best sushi around saiwan hk island. And quite reasonably priced.
Great food
